<h1>Dice Game</h1>
<h2>Welcome.</h2>

Here are the rules:
<p>
	Roll the dice to start the game.
</p>
<p>
	If your first roll is a 7 or 11, you win.
</p>

<p>
	If your first roll is a 2, 3 or 12, you lose.
</p>
<p>
	Anything else becomes your point. Roll your point again before a 7 and you win.
</p>

